    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316540/extras/70ef490a70740ff4fc1fc11d3c07e608.avif?t=1735232204\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316540/extras_big/70ef490a70740ff4fc1fc11d3c07e608.avif?t=1735232204 width=800 height=378 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome aboard to Nubby's Number Factory! This is an arcade roguelike game where you work at a number factory and have to launch Nubby, a spherical humanoid down a peg board to rack up points and produce numbers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316540/extras/f56186cb96df7394e3c820446abb5b14.avif?t=1735232204\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316540/extras_big/f56186cb96df7394e3c820446abb5b14.avif?t=1735232204 width=800 height=264 /></span>In this demo you'll find:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-A complete tutorial</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-60 levels</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-23 unique items to be discovered</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-17 unique perks that modify your runs</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-5 bosses (3 per game)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-7 special events </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-7 different pegboard layouts</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
